{"tid":1720720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文革式既人民鬥人民要點拆？","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T13:57:25.000Z","uid":45250,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"208efc9afe84b5dc5d3296efa9d5fdff71d29403","tid":1720720,"uid":45250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"隨住港共既頂唔L緊，開始要派人打人殺人，要我地香港人內鬥分化，要點樣先拆到中共既仆乖手段？<br />\n<br />\n只係堅持不割席感覺唔太可行，佢正面劈埋黎你都係要反抗都係要擋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然諗到我地文宣要加強，要快D拉攏藍絲，呢個似乎比較有效？<br />\n幫手推上去，係大家呢幾日尚算小勝之時一定要諗定之後既對築，中共無乜幾多手牌，我地過埋呢關中共就收皮，同我推上去，一齊諗計。<br />\n<br />\n天滅中共<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫時諗到：<br />\n1. 堅持不割席<br />\n2. 加強文宣 拉攏藍絲  (可禮拜六日做文宣日)</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QuuGAPb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQuuGAPb.jpg&h=9a1f2102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35b1e4fd595b665e7e196df4c7947277318ff020","tid":1720720,"uid":45250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我個腦好廢 一定要有共識點拆 再而諗埋口號 放係文宣度<br />\n要好似不割呢個意識咁傳開 我地先過到呢一關 <br />\n手足 頂撚住</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0170ff3a183e8e32113360a2ed5bf730f11df89b","tid":1720720,"uid":111637,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRL6MWd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRL6MWd.png&h=425ccb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o5UfFge.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo5UfFge.png&h=c7289d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9g2kgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9g2kgf.jpg&h=efcdf0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBQ24HV.jpg\" d